assert_eq!("\n Hello\tworld", s.trim_end());
```

[Run](https://play.rust-lang.org/?code=%23!%5Ballow(unused)%5D%0Afn+main()+%7B%0A++++let+s+=+%22%5Cn+Hello%5Ctworld%5Ct%5Cn%22;%0A++++assert_eq!(%22%5Cn+Hello%5Ctworld%22,+s.trim_end());%0A%7D&edition=2021)

Directionality:

```
