Returns a string slice with all prefixes and suffixes that match a pattern repeatedly removed.

The [pattern](str/pattern/index.html "mod std::str::pattern") can be a [`char`](primitive.char.html "primitive char"), a slice of [`char`](primitive.char.html "primitive char")s, or a function or closure that determines if a character matches.

##### [Â§](#examples-47)Examples

Simple patterns:

```
