```

[Run](https://play.rust-lang.org/?code=%23!%5Ballow(unused)%5D%0Afn+main()+%7B%0A++++assert_eq!(%2211foo1bar11%22.trim_matches(%271%27),+%22foo1bar%22);%0A++++assert_eq!(%22123foo1bar123%22.trim_matches(char::is_numeric),+%22foo1bar%22);%0A++++%0A++++let+x:+%26%5B_%5D+=+%26%5B%271%27,+%272%27%5D;%0A++++assert_eq!(%2212foo1bar12%22.trim_matches(x),+%22foo1bar%22);%0A%7D&edition=2021)

A more complex pattern, using a closure:

